NAME

    Git::Repository::Plugin::File - Add a file() method to Git::Repository

VERSION

    version 0.002

SYNOPSIS

        use Git::Repository qw(File);
    
        my $repo = Git::Repository->new();
        my $file = $repo->file('lib', 'Git', 'Repository', 'Plugin', 'File.pm');

DESCRIPTION

    Adds a file method to the Git::Repository object that returns a
    Git::Repository::File object.

METHODS

    Git::Repository::Plugin::File adds the following method:

 file(<dir1>, <dir2>, ..., <file>)

    Returns a Git::Repository::File object which behavies like a
    Path::Class::File with a few additional methods;

SEE ALSO

    Git::Repository, Git::Repository::File, Path::Class::File

